measurements.description: Twenty-five crowded flowers on one arching, unsupported 56-cm inflorescence; sepals chartreuse, light burgundy midline distal half; petals slightly recurved, chartreuse, light burgundy midline proximal half; lip recurved, yellow, spotted burgundy apically, keels bright yellow; column light yellow anterior, suffused light burgundy, anther cap white overlaid burgundy; substance firm; texture matte.
